@node Introduction "Neon: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Neon is a plugin for the famous image-manipulation-program
   ArtEffect2/3+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect's
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   Neon is a fun-filter. It has a nice effect.
   Strongly depending on the picture (best on real photos with strong edges,
   e.g. buildings). Edges are becoming a shiny, transparent look and colored
   hem.

@endnode

